snippet.title: Electro Air Hockey - Tournament | Full Walkthrough [ PC ]
snippet.description:
Electro Air Hockey - Tournament | Full Walkthrough (PC) - GMC X1.
" Electro Air Hockey " is a fun air hockey game. This game allows you to experience the same thrill that you can have playing a real life air hockey game! The object is to hit the puck into your opponent’s goal on the opposite side of the table. The speed at which you move the mallet determines the strength of your hit. The first player to score seven points wins. Challenge 10 artificial intelligence players in a linear Tournament Mode and unlock new secret characters!
